{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Getting Started","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"MStore Pro - Complete React Native template for e-commerce","meta_description":"Professional Mobile Store Solution for your business â€“ supports to convert your current WooCommerce website to mobile store app easily","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"mstore","toc":null,"keywords":["mstore","mstore pro","woocommerce app","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"requisite-setup\"><a href=\"#requisite-setup\" aria-label=\"requisite setup permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Requisite setup</h2>\n<p>As the app is required connect with the Wordpress site and WooCommerce plugin via <strong>Rest API,</strong> please refer to the <a href=\"http://woocommerce.github.io/woocommerce-rest-api-docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Rest Document </a>for more detail info</p>\n<p>For easy to config the Wordpress site, you can download the site from <a href=\"http://github.com/inspireui/mstorethis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://github.com/inspireui/mstore</a>, this was already config and install all plugin that use for the app, or if you have your existing website, you can following by below setting.</p>\n<h2 id=\"wordpress-plugins-install\"><a href=\"#wordpress-plugins-install\" aria-label=\"wordpress plugins install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Wordpress Plugins install</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/json-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>JSON API</strong></a>: A RESTful API for WordPress, this plugin is used for only the registration feature (other request from the API we use default REST API from Wordpress site)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/inspireui/mstore/tree/master/plugins/mstore-checkout\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Mstore CheckOut Plugin and API</strong></a>: Extends the JSON API User for RESTful user registration, authentication, support all Payment Gateway, and also comment rating.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-rest-api-featured-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Better Rest API Featured Image</strong></a>: for some reason the image is not populate correctly so that need to install this plugin to support to show the image. </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/onesignal-free-web-push-notifications/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>OneSignal Push Notifications</strong></a> (optional)<strong>:</strong> push notify to the mobile app, or web using OneSignal dashboard admin. This feature is support on Pro version.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/regenerate-thumbnails/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Regenerate Thumbnails</strong></a> (optional)<strong>:</strong> allows you to regenerate all thumbnails after changing the thumbnail sizes, use for customize the app performance when load the product images files (see detail at the step 2 - config.js)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To support multi languages feature, following feature should be install<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"> </a>(optional):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WPML 3.4 or above</li>\n<li>WPML String Translation 2.0 or above</li>\n<li>WPML Translation Management 2.2 or above</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>WooCommerce Multilingual</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpml-to-wp-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>WPML to WP API</strong></a>: use for multi language feature, this api will support to change the product/title/category base on the select language from WPML plugin</li>\n<li>Detail document: <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/related-projects/woocommerce-multilingual\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>click here</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Download all required plugins from: <a href=\"https://github.com/inspireui/mstore/tree/master/plugins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/inspireui/mstore/tree/master/plugins</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"enable-worpdress-setting\"><a href=\"#enable-worpdress-setting\" aria-label=\"enable worpdress setting permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable Worpdress setting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"permalink-url-setting\"><a href=\"#permalink-url-setting\" aria-label=\"permalink url setting permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Permalink URL setting</strong>:</h3>\n<p>Go to <strong>Common Setting</strong>, change the URL to <strong>Post name</strong>, this is required for the setting otherwise some images could not loading.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blobscdn.gitbook.com/v0/b/gitbook-28427.appspot.com/o/assets%2F-LH63EuJG5iAEZIHCZ4d%2F-LH6G6VCreOaKz_HeIDY%2F-LH6UtG7qyjk2N7UBBAq%2FScreen%20Shot%202018-07-11%20at%2011.00.28%20AM.png?alt=media&#x26;token=56fff28f-c10b-44fe-848d-a9d8288f12d0\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>Permalink URL setting</p>\n<h3 id=\"membership-registration\"><a href=\"#membership-registration\" aria-label=\"membership registration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Membership registration</strong>:</h3>\n<p>Enable the option <strong>Anyone</strong> can register.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blobscdn.gitbook.com/v0/b/gitbook-28427.appspot.com/o/assets%2F-LH63EuJG5iAEZIHCZ4d%2F-LH6G6VCreOaKz_HeIDY%2F-LH6LDW-dbhv2jlFhe0F%2FScreen%20Shot%202018-07-11%20at%2010.18.16%20AM.png?alt=media&#x26;token=f452d0e3-4e56-497a-9255-16487b065cd6\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>Membership registration</p>\n<h3 id=\"enable-the-rest-api-controller\"><a href=\"#enable-the-rest-api-controller\" aria-label=\"enable the rest api controller permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable the Rest Api controller</h3>\n<p>This option should be enabled to support the registration and multi payment gateway</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://blobscdn.gitbook.com/v0/b/gitbook-28427.appspot.com/o/assets%2F-LH63EuJG5iAEZIHCZ4d%2F-LH6G6VCreOaKz_HeIDY%2F-LH6VyR7YDYbXlJGYgYr%2FScreen%20Shot%202018-07-11%20at%2011.05.14%20AM.png?alt=media&#x26;token=58c467c3-579f-4d7b-b02a-2bbafe60582b\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>Enable the Rest Api controller</p>\n<h3 id=\"app-config\"><a href=\"#app-config\" aria-label=\"app config permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>App config</h3>\n<p>Go the mstore project folder (mstore-expo or mstore-pro), open the file: <strong>src/common/Config.js</strong> and follow 3 simple steps to setup the app.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 1: change to your website URL and the wooCommerce API consumeKey </li>\n<li>Step 2: Setting Product Images </li>\n<li>Step 3: Config image for the Payment Gateway</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://blobscdn.gitbook.com/v0/b/gitbook-28427.appspot.com/o/assets%2F-LH63EuJG5iAEZIHCZ4d%2F-LH6G6VCreOaKz_HeIDY%2F-LH6Xa21-JOxSuqkZtQ7%2FScreen%20Shot%202018-07-11%20at%2011.12.16%20AM.png?alt=media&#x26;token=1d7f1c1d-accb-4184-9c67-35c9ccbb675e\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>These steps are clarify from the config file, please follow the guide from these style for the customize config.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/mstore/wordpress-setting/"},"timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"Requisite setup As the app is required connect with the Wordpress site and WooCommerce plugin via  Rest API,  please refer to the  Restâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/tony/Beo/inspireui-documents/docs/content/mstore/wordpress-setting.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/mstore/wordpress-setting/"}}